{"tid":487034,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"去快餐店睇盡港人醜態","createTime":"2017-12-02T11:30:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T14:17:38.000Z","uid":153790,"like":21,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a8fe001dd6d6e6412a58962e0a861b3e2faf0666","tid":487034,"uid":153790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T11:30:32.000Z","msg":"今晚自己一個食火鍋<br />\n大概18:30去到 已經full得好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有侍應呀姐幫我搵到個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為一個人易搵<br />\n一坐底 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n格離個港女西面+拉開張枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢老母即刻講：咁又唔洗拉開既<br />\n個港女繼續西面食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個重點係 條女望落去得10零歲<br />\n頂盡中一、中二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你老味 咁撚細個學人西面玩杯葛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚冇家教<br />\n食食下係自己個袋拎d野食出黎淥<br />\n手快快 靜靜雞咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要偷望我有無發現 <br />\n你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關我撚事咩？<br />\n唔通走去告發你？<br />\n不過佢咁撚西 真係有咁既衝動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再望耐d佢個西樣 <br />\n真係無表情都西緊面 <br />\n天生西面女仔真係好撚難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個樣係好衰好衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大個一定係臭雞<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd5beffb8e8362aad